   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Twenty-first year of Marcus Aurelius Commodus Antoninus Augustus (month, day). Herodes son of N.N. [paid to N.N.] and his colleagues, collectors of money taxes, for the poll-tax of the same year at Tebtunis twelve silver drachmas, that is, 12; [Month, Day?] eight [silver] drachmas, that is, 8.</ab>
         </div>
